Usage: setSelectedPtnPinGuide [-help] <x1> <y1> <x2> <y2> <ptnPinObj> <layerID>
                              <space> <cellName>

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<x1>                                # X1 (float, required)
<y1>                                # Y1 (float, required)
<x2>                                # X2 (float, required)
<y2>                                # Y2 (float, required)
<ptnPinObj>                         # name of the net, net group, or pin group
                                    # associated with this pin guide
                                    # (string, required)
<layerID>                           # metal layer(s) for the pin guide
                                    # (string, required)
<space>                             # Spacing (float, required)
<cellName>                          # name of the cell with which the pin group
                                    # is associated (string, required)